      &lt;li&gt;For example, I select “Countries”, and then instead I want to select companies&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;I would have to “zoom out” of countries, and then select “Companies” – two clicks!&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;This problem could be solved by replacing circle with tabs&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;However, this would introduce another problem
