      <item>
        <title>Today&#39;s Optimisations</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;Mid-morning update on today’s optimizations:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Gzip compression for all interaction with server
    &lt;ul&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Bandwidth reduction of 75%&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Overall summary size down to 150Kb from 700Kb&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Hence, speed of getting a response from server up 4 times&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Precalculation of search section combinations
    &lt;ul&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Various section combinations results are precalculated (kept alive)&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;This applies to different time periods (selected at the top)&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Summaries should on average now load in 2 seconds&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
